name: Titu
description:
Fifth stop of my Interstellar Journey; Surprisingly, I found myself floating between small planets, the transition was not what I expected. I think I'm entering a new phase of my life I never expected to get to, almost like the light I always searched for is in front of me. I left my ship behind, and decided to live the experience to its fullest extent from now on.
